  m_text: 'Game Objective:

    Collect all the energy cores in the level, then enter
    the exit door.

    Controls:

    A / D : Move left/right

    Space : Jump

    Touching
    red lasers: Restart

    Touching enemies: Game over

    After collecting all
    energy cores: Exit door opens

    Tips:

    Watch the enemies'' patrol routes
    and time your moves to get through.'
